data.description: *OFFER DEADLINE: SUNDAY, FEB 6TH @10AM* Stunning home, custom designed by sellers. Every detail considered as evidenced by high end champagne & black fixtures & hardware, carefully selected water resistant laminate flooring, gorgeous tile, quartz ctops, 8 ft. doors, wood burning FP, crown molding, can lighting, low E-tilt in sash windows, stained vent hood, farmhouse apron-front sink, expanded master closet attached to utility room, wired for surround sound, expanded driveway, oversized 3-car garage w-epoxy finished flooring, sprinkler system, & the list goes on. Home offers 4 bed, 3 bath, gameroom & office. 4th bedroom has a great mother in law design w-ensuite bathroom. Floorplan & features here are amazing.
